                            <comment id="13174854" author="dvryaboy" created="Thu, 22 Dec 2011 15:47:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Before:&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Tests run: 7, Failures: 0, Errors: 0, Time elapsed: 265.151 sec&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After:&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Tests run: 7, Failures: 0, Errors: 0, Time elapsed: 78.441 sec&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13174954" author="julienledem" created="Thu, 22 Dec 2011 18:24:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 I love fast (ahem, at least faster) unit tests&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13174975" author="dvryaboy" created="Thu, 22 Dec 2011 19:08:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Converted a few more. Full list:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;TestDataBagAccess.java&lt;br/&gt;
TestBatchAliases.java&lt;br/&gt;
TestUTF8.java&lt;br/&gt;
TestPONegative.java&lt;br/&gt;
TestPruneColumn.java&lt;br/&gt;
TestUnion.java&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13175001" author="daijy" created="Thu, 22 Dec 2011 19:38:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Instead of:&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;new PigServer(ExecType.LOCAL, cluster.getProperties())&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
We should use:&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;new PigServer(ExecType.LOCAL, new Properties())&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can also remove &quot;buildCluster&quot; in those tests&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13175003" author="dvryaboy" created="Thu, 22 Dec 2011 19:42:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Julien just pointed out the same thing to me. Updated patch coming soon &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13175106" author="dvryaboy" created="Thu, 22 Dec 2011 22:10:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Gonna commit this. Also a bunch of whitespace changes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13175687" author="daijy" created="Sat, 24 Dec 2011 07:40:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;See some unit test failures. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2448&quot; title=&quot;Convert more tests to use LOCAL mode&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2448&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2448&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.4.patch is the fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13175750" author="dvryaboy" created="Sat, 24 Dec 2011 17:51:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;That&apos;s odd, they were passing on my system. Why doesn&apos;t System.getProperties() work? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13175756" author="daijy" created="Sat, 24 Dec 2011 19:07:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I guess it expose Pig to system environment settings. I see build fail in our internal build machine and my own laptop.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
